## 1. Database Schema Design

### User
```
{
  name, email, password (hashed), phone,
  role: enum ['resident','business_owner','admin'],
  location: { type: 'Point', coordinates: [lng, lat] },  // 2dsphere index
  address, avatar (Cloudinary URL),
  reputationScore: Number (default 0),
  badges: [ObjectId -> Badge],
  isVerified: Boolean,
  societyCode: String (optional, for closed-community feature),
  createdAt, updatedAt
}
```

### Business
```
{
  owner: ObjectId -> User,
  name, category (enum: cafe, restaurant, medical, grocery, salon, other),
  description,
  location: { type: 'Point', coordinates: [lng, lat] },  // 2dsphere index
  address,
  images: [String] (Cloudinary URLs),
  offers: [{ title, description, validTill }],
  avgRating: Number,
  reviewCount: Number,
  isVerified: Boolean,
  verificationDoc: String (Cloudinary URL),
  openingHours: { open, close },
  createdAt
}
```

### Review
```
{
  business: ObjectId -> Business,
  user: ObjectId -> User,
  rating: Number (1-5),
  comment: String,
  images: [String],
  createdAt
}
```

### Activity
```
{
  organizer: ObjectId -> User,
  type (enum: sport, gym, cycling, walking, study, gaming, other),
  title, description,
  location: { type: 'Point', coordinates: [lng, lat] },
  scheduledTime: Date,
  isRecurring: Boolean,
  recurrenceRule: String (optional, e.g. "daily-6am"),
  capacity: Number,
  status: enum ['open', 'matched', 'closed'],   // <-- the toggle field
  createdAt
}
```

### ActivityParticipant
```
{
  activity: ObjectId -> Activity,
  user: ObjectId -> User,
  status: enum ['interested','joined','left'],
  joinedAt
}
```

### Group (Neighborhood/Society)
```
{
  name, description, societyCode (unique),
  location: { type: 'Point', coordinates },
  admins: [ObjectId -> User],
  members: [ObjectId -> User],
  createdAt
}
```

### Post (announcements/discussions/service recommendations)
```
{
  group: ObjectId -> Group,
  author: ObjectId -> User,
  type: enum ['announcement','discussion','recommendation'],
  title, content, images: [String],
  upvotes: [ObjectId -> User],
  downvotes: [ObjectId -> User],
  comments: [{ user, text, createdAt }],
  createdAt
}
```

### Event
```
{
  group: ObjectId -> Group,
  organizer: ObjectId -> User,
  title, description, images: [String],
  location: { type: 'Point', coordinates },
  dateTime: Date,
  createdAt
}
```

### RSVP
```
{
  event: ObjectId -> Event,
  user: ObjectId -> User,
  status: enum ['going','interested','not_going'],
}
```

### LostFound
```
{
  reportedBy: ObjectId -> User,
  type: enum ['lost','found'],
  title, description, images: [String],
  location: { type: 'Point', coordinates },
  category, status: enum ['open','resolved'],
  createdAt
}
```

### Notification
```
{
  user: ObjectId -> User,
  type: enum ['activity','business','group','event','system'],
  message, link, isRead: Boolean,
  createdAt
}
```

### Message (chat)
```
{
  activity: ObjectId -> Activity (or roomId),
  sender: ObjectId -> User,
  content, createdAt
}
```

### Badge
```
{
  name, description, icon, thresholdPoints: Number
}
```

**Indexes:** `2dsphere` on all `location` fields. Compound index on `Activity.status + scheduledTime`. Text index on `Business.name` and `Post.title` for search.

