## 2. Authentication & Authorization

- JWT-based auth (access token + refresh token in httpOnly cookie), OR Clerk if you want faster setup — pick one, don't do both.
- Middleware: `authMiddleware` (verifies token), `roleCheck(['business_owner'])` (restricts routes by role).
- Roles: `resident`, `business_owner`, `admin`.
- Registration flow captures location (via browser geolocation) and stores as GeoJSON Point.
- Password hashing via bcrypt, rate-limited login route to prevent brute force.

