## 4. Socket.io Event Design

**Namespaces/rooms:**
- `activity:{activityId}` — chat + live participant updates + status toggle broadcast
- `user:{userId}` — personal notification channel
- `presence` — global online/offline tracking

**Events:**
| Event | Direction | Payload |
|---|---|---|
| `join_activity_room` | client→server | `{ activityId }` |
| `activity_message` | client→server | `{ activityId, content }` |
| `new_message` | server→client | `{ sender, content, timestamp }` |
| `participant_joined` | server→client | `{ userId, name }` |
| `participant_left` | server→client | `{ userId }` |
| `activity_status_changed` | server→client | `{ activityId, status }` — fired when organizer toggles found/closed |
| `typing` / `stop_typing` | both | `{ activityId, userId }` |
| `user_online` / `user_offline` | server→client | `{ userId }` |
| `new_notification` | server→client | `{ notification }` |

