## 9. Build Phases (Recommended Order)

### Phase 0 — Foundation (Days 1-2)
- Repo setup, folder structure, env config, DB connection, base Express app, base Vite app, Tailwind setup, CORS, error-handling middleware.

### Phase 1 — Auth & User System (Days 3-5)
- Register/login/logout, JWT middleware, role-based access, profile page, geolocation capture on signup.

### Phase 2 — Business Discovery (Days 6-10)
- Business CRUD, image upload, geospatial search, reviews, ratings, search & filters, business owner dashboard, basic analytics.

### Phase 3 — Activity Partners (Days 11-16) — **Flagship module**
- Activity CRUD, geospatial matching query, join/leave flow, status toggle (open/matched/closed), Socket.io room setup, real-time chat, live participant updates, typing indicators, presence tracking.

### Phase 4 — Community & Groups (Days 17-22)
- Group creation/join via code, posts (announcements/discussions/recommendations), voting, comments, events + RSVP, lost & found board.

### Phase 5 — Notifications, Reputation, PWA (Days 23-26)
- Notification system + Socket push, reputation engine + badges, PWA manifest + service worker + Web Push.

### Phase 6 — Polish & Deployment (Days 27-30)
- Global search, admin moderation panel, responsive QA, loading/error states, deployment (Vercel for client, Render/Railway for server, MongoDB Atlas, Cloudinary), environment variable audit, final testing.

